'''巴基斯坦塔利班运动'''（{{lang-ur|تحریک طالبان پاکستان}}），通稱'''巴基斯坦塔利班'''或'''巴塔'''，是[[南亚|南亚]]国家[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]的一个[[伊斯兰|伊斯兰]][[军队|军事组织]]，被[[美国政府|美国政府]]、[[英国政府|英国政府]]和[[加拿大政府|加拿大政府]]列入[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]组织名单<ref name='yusufzai20080922'>{{cite journal | title = A Who's Who of the Insurgency in Pakistan's North-West Frontier Province: Part One – North and South Waziristan | journal = Terrorism Monitor | date = 2008-09-22 | first = Rahimullah | last = Yusufzai | volume = 6 | issue = 18 | id =  | url = http://www.jamestown.org/programs/gta/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=5169&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=167&no_cache=1 | accessdate = 2011-03-30 | archive-date = 2010-12-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20101226171217/http://www.jamestown.org/programs/gta/single/?tx_ttnews%5Btt_news%5D=5169&tx_ttnews%5BbackPid%5D=167&no_cache=1 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。它建立于2007年12月，创始人名叫[[贝图拉·马哈苏德|贝图拉·马哈苏德]]，大约有1万名成员（也有人估計為3萬至3萬5千名成員），地盘主要是巴基斯坦西北部<ref name=Bajoria>{{cite web| last = Bajoria| first = Jayshree| title = Pakistan's New Generation of Terrorists| publisher = Council on Foreign Relations| date = 2008-02-06| url = http://www.cfr.org/publication/15422/pakistans_new_generation_of_terrorists.html?breadcrumb=%2Fbios%2F13611%2Fjayshree_bajoria%3Fgroupby%3D1%26hide%3D1%26id%3D13611%26filter%3D456| accessdate = 2009-03-30| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090514060717/http://www.cfr.org/publication/15422/pakistans_new_generation_of_terrorists.html?breadcrumb=%2Fbios%2F13611%2Fjayshree_bajoria%3Fgroupby%3D1&hide=1&id=13611&filter=456| archivedate = 2009年5月14日}}</ref><ref name=gall2009327>{{cite news| author =[[Carlotta_Gall|Carlotta Gall]], Ismail Khan, [[Pir_Zubair_Shah|Pir Zubair Shah]] and Taimoor Shah| title =Pakistani and Afghan Taliban Unify in Face of U.S. Influx| work =New York Times| date =2009-03-26| url =http://www.nytimes.com/2009/03/27/world/asia/27taliban.html| accessdate =2009-03-27| archive-date =2021-01-28| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20210128